values.description: to point to static website in the bucket
values.name: terraform-gcp

website_bucket_name.description: The name of the Google Cloud Storage bucket hosting the website.

website_bucket_url.description: The URL of the website hosted on the GCS bucket.

website_cdn_backend_name.description: The name of the CDN backend bucket.

website_cdn_enabled.description: Whether CDN is enabled for the backend bucket.

website_dns_name.description: The DNS name of the website.

website_dns_record.description: The DNS A record pointing to the website's static IP.

website_http_forwarding_rule.description: The name and IP address of the HTTP forwarding rule.

website_http_redirect_proxy_name.description: The name of the HTTP-to-HTTPS redirect proxy.

website_https_forwarding_rule.description: The name and IP address of the HTTPS forwarding rule.

website_https_proxy_name.description: The name of the HTTPS proxy for the website.

website_ssl_certificate_domains.description: The domains covered by the SSL certificate.

website_ssl_certificate_name.description: The name of the managed SSL certificate.

website_ssl_policy_min_tls_version.description: The minimum TLS version enforced by the SSL policy.

website_ssl_policy_name.description: The name of the SSL policy applied to the HTTPS proxy.

website_static_ip.description: The static IP address reserved for the website.

website_url.description: The full URL of the website.
